details.description: B&K Tea Cafe was established on the basics of quality, efficiency, and consistency. B&K uses the highest quality syrups, tea leaves, and powders for every hand crafted bubble tea. We pride ourselves in our passion and make it our goal to exceed our customers' expectations. B&K and its staff are determined to provide a positive experience by ensuring a quick, friendly visit every time. We at B&K Tea Cafe are a locally owned and operated business who hopes to serve you soon.

reviews_data.review_text: Such a nice little place to get boba! Great service and got my drinks fairly quick. Definitely my go to boba place in Mooresville!

Well ordered extremely sweet strawberry matcha. Felt nauseus from all that ssugar in it. Asked for replacemant. Was denied w not friendly stuff. They said they called owner guy which said i can not change my drink just for green matcha w sugar like 25-50%. Cashier came to me to tell me that i cant have replacement and  while talked to me she very loudly cracked her fingers on her both hands right in my face. It was supernasty Careless and not customer service for regular customer. Will go now on to another boba place clpse by. How someone let u stuck w something what u dont enjoy?!!! Im very disappointed after i spent here so much money w my kids!!!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Helena, 

I am sorry you were unsatisfied with our customer service this one time. We have served you many times and bent to your many unreasonable requests a myriad of times. We pride our staff on being very friendly and customer oriented as you can see from the other 200+ reviews but we will not tolerate disrespect to our staff in OUR store. Please choose to shop elsewhere because we like to accommodate to our customers that appreciate us and our staff. 

- B&K Management

reviews_data.review_text:
I shamelessly drive here from Mint Hill for my large Taro. The ladies are always pleasant.

UPDATE 8/23: Bobby, co-founder of the company, reached out to me to rectify the issue I had prior. He assured that the team was notified of the consistency concern, and that reflected in the drink I got yesterday 8/22. The Taro milk tea that I received reminded me of why it’s indeed still my favorite place, and Bobby’s willingness to ensure good customer service made a lasting impression. Leo worked the register, and I didn’t catch the name of the young person who made my drink but they were blonde with a cherry-design hair claw. As usual, the drink was ready within a minute or two of ordering. Looking forward to my next visit. Thank you Bobby and team!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Sherika,

I am so glad you enjoy B&K! We are saddened to hear that your most recent visits haven’t been up to par with your first experiences. Please email mooresville@bkteacafe.com and we will compensate you for 2 free drinks for the trouble. Thank you and I hope to hear from you. I will notify our staff of the inconsistency and have this fixed right away.

-B&K Management

reviews_data.owner_answer:
Helena, 

I am sorry you were unsatisfied with our customer service this one time. We have served you many times and bent to your many unreasonable requests a myriad of times. We pride our staff on being very friendly and customer oriented as you can see from the other 200+ reviews but we will not tolerate disrespect to our staff in OUR store. Please choose to shop elsewhere because we like to accommodate to our customers that appreciate us and our staff. 

- B&K Management

reviews_data.review_text:
I shamelessly drive here from Mint Hill for my large Taro. The ladies are always pleasant.

UPDATE 8/23: Bobby, co-founder of the company, reached out to me to rectify the issue I had prior. He assured that the team was notified of the consistency concern, and that reflected in the drink I got yesterday 8/22. The Taro milk tea that I received reminded me of why it’s indeed still my favorite place, and Bobby’s willingness to ensure good customer service made a lasting impression. Leo worked the register, and I didn’t catch the name of the young person who made my drink but they were blonde with a cherry-design hair claw. As usual, the drink was ready within a minute or two of ordering. Looking forward to my next visit. Thank you Bobby and team!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Sherika,

I am so glad you enjoy B&K! We are saddened to hear that your most recent visits haven’t been up to par with your first experiences. Please email mooresville@bkteacafe.com and we will compensate you for 2 free drinks for the trouble. Thank you and I hope to hear from you. I will notify our staff of the inconsistency and have this fixed right away.

-B&K Management
